title: Re-engineering to create UML Diagrams from .NET binary assembly
content:
What is the base way to generate UML diagrams (both class and sequence) from .NET assembly using OpenSource tools?
The 200% Reflective Class Diagram Creation Tool cannot be used due on problems starting custom build on machine.
Ready-to use builds needed.

comments.text: All Reflector addins are not up-to-date
Hi and welcome to RE.SE. You may edit your own question if you have further information to add. Comments are intentionally volatile and may disappear in the future without notice.
